message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product. It's a high-quality item that we believe would be very valuable to you. Considering its worth to us, I'd like to propose an offer of $150 for it. Please let me know if this is within your budget.
I appreciate your offer, but I'm looking to save some money. I'd like to make a counteroffer of $120 for the product. I think it's a great item, but I'm not willing to pay the full $150.
